Why are not any of the other constituents of the virus-toxic stressors combination nexus being placed under effective ‘quarantine’ from the public? Why are not smoking, or air pollution, or excess alcohol, or wireless radiation, or agrochemicals, or industrial chemicals, being placed under quarantine? There is no lack of evidence of linkages between these environmental pollutants and immune-related diseases (
 Tsatsakis et al., 2020; 
 Kostoff et al., 2020).
